cz.syntea.xdef

Interface XDContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<XDValue>, XDValue, XDValueID
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    XDElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    XDElementAbstract

    public interface XDContainer
extends XDValue
    Map of named items and sequence items in x-script. Contains both, the table of named items and the sequence of items.

      • sortXD

        XDContainer sortXD(java.lang.String key,
                   boolean asc)
        Sorts this context.
        Parameters:
